casebody.data:
Emma Christionsen, Respondent, v. William Fulwider et al., Appellants. Adolph Christionsen, Respondent, v. William Fulwider et al., Appellants.

Order affirmed, without costs of this appeal to any party. All concur. (The order grants plaintiffs’ motion to restore each of two automobile negligence actions to the ready calendar, and denies cross motions of defendants to dismiss the complaints.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Dowling, McCurn, Larkin and Love, JJ.
